  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DomainCreateResponse
extends CreateResponse
    Use this to access create data for a domain as provided in an EPP domain create response compliant with RFC5730 and RFC5731. Such a service element is sent by a compliant EPP server in response to a valid domain create command, implemented by the DomainCreateCommand.
    See Also:
    DomainCreateCommand, Serialized Form
